OL,4,Cgenerations as landmark bill voted
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,FPeople turning 18 from 2027 will never
OL,8,Fbe able to legally buy cigarettes in
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FThat's after the Senedd voted to pass
OL,12,Fa landmark Bill affecting anyone born
OL,13,Fon or after January 1, 2009.
OL,15,FFrom 2027, it will become illegal to
OL,16,Fsell tobacco to anyone who is 18 years
OL,17,Fold.
