OL,7,FSmoking is the leading cause of
OL,8,Fpreventable ill health and premature
OL,9,Fdeath in Wales, with around 5,000
OL,10,Fdeaths a year as a result. The
OL,11,Flegislation has already been passed in
OL,12,FScotland and Northern Ireland, meaning
OL,13,Fit can be implemented there once it
OL,14,Freceives Royal Assent from the King.
