OL,7,FThe Bill was introduced by the UK
OL,8,FGovernment, but needed Senedd approval
OL,9,Fas health is a devolved matter. It is
OL,10,Fhoped that this new law will help
OL,11,FWales reach its 2030 smoke-free
OL,12,Ftarget. This is defined as 5% or less
OL,13,Fof the adult population smoking.
