OL,7,FMental Health and Wellbeing Minister
OL,8,FSarah Murphy said: "This is a historic
OL,9,Fday for public health in Wales.
OL,10,FDespite the real progress we have made
OL,11,Fto reduce smoking levels, tobacco
OL,12,Fcontinues to be one of the leading
OL,13,Fcauses of preventable disease and
OL,14,Fpremature death in Wales.
OL,16,F"The Tobacco and Vapes Bill provides
OL,17,Fus with a unique opportunity to tackle
OL,18,Fsmoking and the growing issue of youth
OL,19,Fvaping.
